			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody"><span style="font-weight: bold">Suspend Minion III</span>
<br />
Prerequisite: Level 62. This ability allows a player to suspend a pet they have summoned (i.e. Skeleton, Animation, Warder, Wolf) and bring it back later. The first rank suspends the pet at its current health only, while the second rank suspends the pet with all of its beneficial effects as well as its weapons and armor. <span style="font-weight: bold">The third rank lets you ZONE with a suspended pet at its current health, with all of its beneficial effects as well as its weapons and armor.</span>
<br />

<br />
Always cracks me up to lose my warder when I have to zone and I seriously cannot picture myself being a warrior having to prepare my weapons after each zoning.
<br />

<br />

