				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">During beta when we were working with the EQ team on our pet issues, they told us that it was impossible to do what you are asking. Basically the system requirment on their side would be too great to allow this to work. So until they completely re-write the EQ engine I doubt you will ever see this. Sorry, not a bad idea but just impractical with the current limitations.<br />_________________<br />Bukar Tigerclaw		
